OL,3,CEurope's largest council could be run
OL,4,Cby a minority as Labour refuse
OL,5,Ccoalition
OL,7,FLabour has ruled out entering a
OL,8,Fcoalition to help run Birmingham City
OL,9,FCouncil, making any path to a working
OL,10,Fmajority even harder.
OL,12,FThe Greens hold 19 councillors, while
OL,13,Fthe Liberal Democrats have 12 -
OL,14,Fleaving the two parties well short of
OL,15,Fthe 51 seats needed for a majority.
OL,17,FReform UK also ruled itself out of
OL,18,Fcoalition talks on Tuesday, saying it
OL,19,Fhad "no viable route" to forming an
OL,20,Fadministration despite being the
OL,21,Flargest group with 23 councillors.
OL,26,@{D@EOU{D@UO]
