OL,3,CEurope's largest council could be run
OL,4,Cby a minority as Labour refuse
OL,5,Ccoalition
OL,7,FLabour's newly selected leader,
OL,8,FCouncillor Nicky Brennan, is in charge
OL,9,Fof the 17 Labour councillors who
OL,10,Fsurvived the vote last week.
OL,12,FCllr Brennan said she respected the
OL,13,Foutcome of the election and
OL,14,Facknowledged voters' frustration with
OL,15,Fthe pace of change at the council.
OL,17,FShe said: "For that reason, our group
OL,18,Fwill not be entering into any
OL,19,Fcoalition agreement or power-sharing
OL,20,Farrangement with other parties.
OL,26,@yD@KOU
