OL,3,CEurope's largest council could be run
OL,4,Cby a minority as Labour refuse
OL,5,Ccoalition
OL,7,F"We will continue to serve residents
OL,8,Fconstructively from the opposition
OL,9,Fbenches, holding the new
OL,10,Fadministration to account where
OL,11,Fnecessary while supporting decisions
OL,12,Fthat are in the best interests of the
OL,13,Fcity and its residents."
OL,15,FThe political stand-off in
OL,16,FWorcestershire has also raised
OL,17,Fquestions about whether Conservatives,
OL,18,Fwho have 16 seats in Birmingham, would
OL,19,Fbe willing or allowed to enter
OL,20,Fcoalition agreements elsewhere.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@XO]
