OL,3,CEurope's largest council could be run
OL,4,Cby a minority as Labour refuse
OL,5,Ccoalition
OL,7,FAt Worcestershire County Council, a
OL,8,Fproposed coalition between the
OL,9,FConservatives, Greens, Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats and independents appeared to
OL,11,Funravel within hours.
OL,13,FThe agreement had initially ousted
OL,14,FReform UK as the controlling group,
OL,15,Fdespite the party winning the most
OL,16,Fseats.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
