OL,3,CEurope's largest council could be run
OL,4,Cby a minority as Labour refuse
OL,5,Ccoalition
OL,7,FBut Conservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Flater suspended local Tory group
OL,9,Fleader Adam Kent, saying the
OL,10,Farrangement had not been authorised by
OL,11,Fparty headquarters.
OL,13,FIn Birmingham, the numbers also make
OL,14,Fforming an administration difficult.
OL,16,FThe first full council meeting since
OL,17,Fthe election is scheduled for Tuesday.
